items.name: Armored Core Wiki
items.title: Armored Core Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Armored Core Wiki!
items.desc:
Armored Core for the PlayStation is the first Armored Core for the system and also the first in the series.

In the presumably distant future, the vast majority of Earth's population is wiped out by a cataclysmic war known as the Great Destruction. The harsh conditions that result force the few remaining survivors to live underground for fifty years, during which time corporations come to power. The two largest corporations, Chrome and Murakumo Millennium, constantly battle each other for supremacy, causing significant strife among the populace. However, the competition provides endless opportunities for the Ravens, mercenaries who exist independently of the corporations. You, the protagonist, are the Raven pilot of an Armored Core (AC), which is a giant mecha.

items.headline: Willkommen im EVE Sister Scanner Wiki
items.desc: EVE Sister Core Scanner Wiki ist eine stetig wachsende Referenz über zufällig auftretende Weltallphänomene im MMOG EVE Online. Diese Anomalien und Signaturen müssen erscannt werden, versorgen dann den EVE Piloten mit allerlei Aufgaben und Kill Missionen u.ä. - und natürlich auch mit entsprechenden Belohnungen. Der Name des Wiki kommt von der wohl besten im Spiel vorhandenen Kombination aus Scanner Probes und dem entsprechenden Launcher: die Sister Core Scanner Probes (Launcher).

items.title: Double Score Wiki
items.headline: Learn more about the Double Score Wiki
items.desc: Double Score is a Japanese otome game that centers around Mai, a seventeen-year-old girl who works at Kamizono Shrine, a shrine surrounded by flowers that grant people blessings. Mai's parents were blessed by these flowers, and she dreams to experience a love like theirs. Little did she know that the flowers would guide her to her fated one.
